{"tid":962421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"等嗶聲響趕覆機時代告終　最後Call機台停運","createTime":"2018-12-30T23:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T11:05:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"76c8c2c07ccff34a3c06b6f73b260dc6729cb855","tid":962421,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:50:13.000Z","msg":"12月30日(日) 15:58更新 12:00建立   <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_01p.jpg?20181230155825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20181230155825&h=1ee691b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本紅星廣末涼子曾擔當傳呼機代言人。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n「嗶嗶&mdash;&mdash;」我們所認識的「BB機、Call機」在日本被暱稱為「口袋鈴」，曾幾何時也是最受歡迎流動通訊設備。不過，隨着手提電話日趨普及，日本最後一間提供傳呼機網絡的電訊公司，已宣布將於明年9月底終止服務。在日本告別「平成」年代（1989年至今）、改朝換代的2019年，曾是上一代人的集體青春回憶亦終需落幕。 <br />\n<br />\n在手提電話、互聯網電郵尚未流行的90年代，傳呼機可說是紅極一時。日本當時更推出過以傳呼機為題材的電視劇《口袋鈴偏偏不響》，同名主題曲亦大受歡迎；日媒甚至形容Call機是平成年代的象徵之一。 <br />\n<br />\n傳呼機普及度之高，讓它聯同泡泡襪、貼紙相手帳，並稱「90年代女高中生三大神器」。趕潮流的高中少女更創作出不少「潮語」，以諧音和數字形狀，編出「14106（我愛你）」、「3470（再見）」等暗號。 <br />\n<br />\n40歲記者岡田有花憶述，自己當年就讀高中時，正值傳呼機流行的全盛時期。她形容當時的Call機就等同現時的智能電話，同學都人手一台，朋友聯絡或談情都少不了它。岡田難忘當年對Call機愛不釋手的時光，即使只是發發「早安」、「我睡了」等沒有營養的內容，也樂此不疲。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，在資訊發達的現今，莫說文字、連聲畫訊息的傳遞也不過是彈指之間的事，新一代人自然再也不需理解那一串串的數字暗號。引入傳呼機的先驅供應商「NTT docomo」，早於2007年就已停止該服務。而2007年，亦正正是iPhone初代面世的一年。 <br />\n<br />\n消息傳出，日本網民紛紛以當年暗號發文懷緬︰「65 05 24 64 04 93，12 71 71 44 04，11 92 21 04 45 13（口袋鈴，至今以來謝謝你了。）」、「81 81（Bye Bye）！」有網民見貼大呼懷念，但亦有不少年輕一代一頭霧水︰「暗號？看不懂啊。」 <br />\n<br />\n在資訊爆炸的年代，傳呼機只能日漸式微，難逃被淘汰的命運。外人也許不會明白，但對於曾經在晚上捏着Call機、在電話亭排隊等「覆機」的那一代人，那種青春時代不再的共鳴與不捨是難以言喻的。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_02p.jpg?20181230155825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_02p.jpg%3F20181230155825&h=46f83891&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18628c4e9db9a174e1f055401d3e4c1657945d08","tid":962421,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_03p.jpg?20181230155825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_03p.jpg%3F20181230155825&h=c7dd5db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_04p.jpg?20181230155825\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230120023300-1230_00912_001_04p.jpg%3F20181230155825&h=f6c56ac1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cf9a4c53c5fcd8080796e7d7db4a5468303008d","tid":962421,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T23:57:24.000Z","msg":"電話停大排長龍既年代"},{"pid":"35750f2d4ab8ccccc0e43bea99939278c2678683","tid":962421,"uid":89683,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:01:33.000Z","msg":"00後不懂操作call 機"},{"pid":"d80ab9b1e89415ee1e04770a45df9cfe564f5a42","tid":962421,"uid":83910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"勾起返自己接觸過兩代call機嘅回憶<br />\n<br />\n第一代：淨係show call你條友個姓氏代號同電話<br />\n第二代：call台會send段留言去傳呼機"},{"pid":"85fb6b66d34b56c61b8b0b09b14c76cdc2185d69","tid":962421,"uid":166885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:15:18.000Z","msg":"香港仲有call機台，放心"},{"pid":"d2ce4a786430090386cabdac6708caf212c9b866","tid":962421,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:25:42.000Z","msg":"關東仍有1500人用傳呼機　電訊商轉型發展防災無線業<br />\n12月30日(日) 13:04   <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/photo/bkn-20181230130454117-1230_00912_001_01p.jpg?20181230135444\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181230130454117-1230_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20181230135444&h=d37acbaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本尚有少部分民眾使用傳呼機。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n雖然Call機通訊的年代不復再，但現時在日本關東仍有1500名用戶使用，相信與人口老化有關，他們仍然使用這些過時的科技產品。傳呼網絡仍能在其他領域派上用場，不少醫院醫生會用傳呼機交流，今後亦會發展防災無線業務。 <br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，傳呼機自1968年7月在東京的23個中心行政區開始營運；由日本電信電話株式會社（NTT）的前身Telephone Public Corp提供服務。傳呼機初期只會發出「嗶嗶」聲響，在1980年代開始顯示數字，繼而衍生出以數字諧音表達的暗碼，其後可以顯示文字及簡單圖案。 <br />\n<br />\n起初，傳呼機售價2000日圓（約141港元），1991年後售價升至5000日圓（約354港元）。用戶每次接獲傳呼後要致電傳呼中心才能知道訊息內容，用戶多為公司行政人員、政府機構等。 <br />\n<br />\n醫生善用傳呼機是因為訊號既不影響精密儀器，在地下及建築物內亦容易接收。最後提供傳呼機服務的東京電訊，其社長清野英俊表示，今後將主力發展防災無線業務，活用傳呼機電波。清野表示，傳呼機時代終結並不令人感到難過寂寞，稱︰「非常感謝至今以來使用過傳呼機的用家。」"},{"pid":"5d3836e7cf4a1550b762622675d4ce2ff0f9a97e","tid":962421,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:27:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/mobile/bkn-20181230130454117-1230_00912_001.html?eventPath=hk_aeanews&amp;eventID=71549E51796BCA45E050007F010049A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20181230%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181230130454117-1230_00912_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_aeanews%26eventID%3D71549E51796BCA45E050007F010049A4&d=4gXlBYZ6EL0HpDvDIV0rjMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1bceff16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20181230/mobile/bkn-20181230130454117-1230_00912_001.html?eventPath=hk_aeanews&amp;eventID=71549E51796BCA45E050007F010049A4</a>"},{"pid":"95e899ef0efd89df0602556f0305002567c73fc9","tid":962421,"uid":182499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"35750f2d4ab8ccccc0e43bea99939278c2678683","tid":962421,"uid":89683,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:01:33.000Z","msg":"00後不懂操作call 機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:35:53.000Z","msg":"我都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 80後"},{"pid":"7379b4784c5799344230ea52828638362cf9da81","tid":962421,"uid":125380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fcd9b83522352f7fe4d2c2f71085b32f3dad7b","tid":962421,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/_14869985445a9e8039a6161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F_14869985445a9e8039a6161.jpg&h=c9f1445c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d65bad77403f57ce056130b1a4453b360b152c6c","tid":962421,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:50:06.000Z","msg":"當年Ｄ雞都活用call機"},{"pid":"9010202b63db21205af7f6e370ede0988e209fc6","tid":962421,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d80ab9b1e89415ee1e04770a45df9cfe564f5a42","tid":962421,"uid":83910,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"勾起返自己接觸過兩代call機嘅回憶<br />\n<br />\n第一代：淨係show call你條友個姓氏代號同電話<br />\n第二代：call台會send段留言去傳呼機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"要搵公共電話覆call機"},{"pid":"80bd55fc3c421786b7668b2a70a05487c634f778","tid":962421,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"好想聽做call台啲人既訪問<br />\n一定好多搞笑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7255604e3b41b01f36e21c7b895a0087464afb02","tid":962421,"uid":98826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"35750f2d4ab8ccccc0e43bea99939278c2678683","tid":962421,"uid":89683,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T00:01:33.000Z","msg":"00後不懂操作call 機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"90後都未必識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37df11cb581470b5e82c4dbe6c849916a3b0df5e","tid":962421,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"80後表示，收call周圍搵電話覆嘅日子真係好奇幻，明明淨係得一個人call 都會成日望住有冇響<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c954d75ae0229f38c8cbac7abddcf85e0223bec","tid":962421,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"老豆用過兩代<br />\n第一代剩數字，佢會有本簿仔你自己翻譯<br />\n第二代可以出埋中文仔<br />\n細個會打去call台叫老豆買魚蛋粉做宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42b66647c35b363813271f36d3d715afe69ef87","tid":962421,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"其實點解香港有仲call機公司，明明手機已經好平，人人都買得起咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b38658461d73a6b2eab0ccc3c9fb16ced7115a","tid":962421,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42b66647c35b363813271f36d3d715afe69ef87","tid":962421,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"其實點解香港有仲call機公司，明明手機已經好平，人人都買得起咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"見醫院醫生仲用call機"},{"pid":"048d03d72bccf60a64ce4d6bf47489296dffefc7","tid":962421,"uid":79728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42b66647c35b363813271f36d3d715afe69ef87","tid":962421,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"其實點解香港有仲call機公司，